People ex rel. Stapleton, Respondent, v. Bell et al., Appellants. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. December 11, 1889.)

Argued before Learned, P. J., and Landon and Fish, JJ.

No opinion. Stay of proceedings vacated. Landon, J., dissenting. For former reports, see 7 N. Y. Supp. 701; ante, 254.
